title: Looking for the perfect place to call home?
posting_body: ['13543 Greenwood Ave N, Seattle, WA 98133', 'Mosaic on Greenwood Mosaic on Greenwood is a perfect combination of comfort and style nestled in the Broadview neighborhood of Seattle, Washington.', 'This gated community has a selection of featured amenities with garage parking and a gorgeous courtyard and pond to enjoy.', 'Spend less time commuting and more time enjoying family, friends, dining out, outdoor adventures, and local entertainment nearby.', 'Discover gorgeous natural scenery including the well-known gem, Carkeek Park.', 'Schedule a tour today to discover your new home at Mosaic on Greenwood.', 'Apartment Features:', 'Energy Efficient Windows', 'Washer & Dryer in Unit', 'All Electric Heat', 'Patio/Balcony', 'Open Concept Floor Plans', 'Unique One and Two Bedroom Floor Plans', 'Community Features:', 'On Metro Bus Route', 'Controlled Access / Gated Community', 'Intercom Entry', 'Elevator', 'Located Near Carkeek Park', 'Translation Service Available', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
